    <dcterms:title>A Modern Purgatory</dcterms:title>
    <dcterms:description>"This book is a record of the prison experiences of Carlo de Fornaro, artist, writer, editor, revolutionary. It is a record of experiences in the famous Tombs prison, in New York City, and in the New York City penitentiary on Blackwell's Island."--Introduction</dcterms:description>
